            <title type="html"><![CDATA[Alert]]></title>
            <link href="/molecules/alert/"/>
            <updated>2019-09-07T23:52:58+02:00</updated>
            <id>/molecules/alert/</id>
            <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div id="myalert"></div>
<script>
    parseComponentHTML("#myalert", {
        "name": "alert",
        "vars": {
            "type": "info",
            "message": "This is an alert"
        }
    });
</script>

<p>An alert message box that fills a container.</p>
<p>The alert type can be any [color] or [color]-[tone] required.</p>
<p>Example for a fixed container with the JS Modal particle:</p>
<p><button class="btn btn-primary w4" onclick='simple_pop("#alert-container", {
                "name": "alert",
                "vars": {
                    "type": "success",
                    "message": "You have opened an alert!"
                }
            })'>Open alert</button></p>

<p>Example API call:</p>
<pre><code>parseComponentHTML("#myalert", {
    "name": "alert",
    "vars": {
        "type": "info",
        "message": "This is an alert"
    }
});
</code></pre>
<p>Code:</p>
<iframe src="https://component.frisovandijk.com/api/source/molecules/alert.mustache" class="w-100 h5 br3 bg-grays-light4"></iframe>
]]></content>
